+# Selector Output - beyond-de-giorgi / run-010
+
+## Full Ranking
+
+1. `Chain 02 - Adapted-Package Geometric Vorticity Route From Local Beltrami Deficit To Criterion Scale`
+2. `Chain 01 - Deterministic Material Stretching Route With Admissible Proxy Freeze`
+3. `Chain 03 - Packet-Complete Helical Interaction Route With Host-Inequality Freeze`
+4. `Chain 04 - Critical Element Program With Pre-Admitted Exact-NS Firewall`
+
+## Selected Portfolio
+
+The strongest three-chain portfolio is:
+
+1. `Chain 02`
+2. `Chain 01`
+3. `Chain 03`
+
+This portfolio maximizes diversity without spending a slot on a dependent reserve architecture.
+
+- `Chain 02` is the best direct mission-facing mechanism hunt. It openly pays for package change, tests persistence under an adapted geometry-aware regime, and forces criterion-scale or contradiction-scale cash-out. Even on failure it should return a sharp obstruction ledger about package theater, hidden derivative debt, or failure to control full stretching.
+- `Chain 01` is the best theorem-floor-disciplined alternative after the stochastic branch died. It keeps the search on deterministic transport structure while forcing an admissible observable, explicit defect accounting, and an LEI/CKN insertion test. Even if it fails, it should produce a useful obstruction about definability, coercivity, or endpoint transfer.
+- `Chain 03` preserves the highest-upside Tao-sensitive path without duplicating the other two. It is the only exact-symbol / packet route, and it now forces one host bad term, one burden currency, complete mixed-helicity restoration, and physical-space reconstruction before any claim survives. Even on failure it should isolate whether the obstruction is setup, ledger completion, mixed-helicity collapse, or reconstruction collapse.
+
+## Why Chain 04 Was Not Selected
+
+`Chain 04` is structurally weaker for adversarial testing at this stage because it does not supply an independent mechanism. Its own Step 1 requires an upstream firewall artifact from another chain, so a large fraction of its failure modes are immediate no-entry verdicts rather than new information about the PDE mechanism hunt. It remains the correct fourth-ranked reserve architecture, but not one of the best three slots for this run.
+
